09:20.859 --> 09:22.069
Mary?

09:24.238 --> 09:25.405
Mary!

09:27.824 --> 09:30.410
Mary, where are you?!

09:30.577 --> 09:33.163
Mary! Mary!

09:34.289 --> 09:36.792
[baby crying in distance]

09:41.838 --> 09:43.674
Don't hurt my wife and baby!

09:46.093 --> 09:48.428
Mary. Mary.

09:48.637 --> 09:50.305
[baby crying]

09:55.936 --> 09:57.354
Come see.

09:57.521 --> 09:59.690
The Savior is born.

10:01.275 --> 10:03.110
[demonic growling]

10:04.569 --> 10:07.406
[screaming] No! No-o-o-o!

10:07.572 --> 10:11.076
