- [zombies growling]

10:11.243 --> 10:13.704
[flesh tearing]

10:18.375 --> 10:21.253
[inhuman sobbing]

10:24.548 --> 10:26.341
[deep growling]

10:27.509 --> 10:29.261
[crying continues]

10:36.101 --> 10:39.271
[zombies moaning]

11:07.549 --> 11:09.509
