11:37.204 --> 11:40.832
Holy crap.
Is that a Zed?

11:40.999 --> 11:43.418
- It's my father.
- Not anymore, kid.

11:43.585 --> 11:46.296
Let me guess.
He tried to eat you,

11:46.505 --> 11:47.881
