a wolf cluck?

17:43.737 --> 17:45.530
[laughs, scoffs]

17:46.990 --> 17:48.658
Who the fuck are you?

17:48.867 --> 17:51.369
I'm Thora.
This is my committed, Magnum.

17:51.536 --> 17:53.663
This is Phoenix and Beset,
who are committed.

17:53.830 --> 17:55.915
- [Girl #1] Committed for what?
- To procreate.

18:03.590 --> 18:06.259
Hold that for me,
would ya, sweetheart?

18:09.554 --> 18:12.599
- Hello, Wolfie.
- Hello.

18:12.766 --> 18:14.392
