works every time.

18:21.399 --> 18:22.776
[grunts]

18:22.942 --> 18:24.194
He's mine.

18:24.402 --> 18:26.196
[laughing]

18:27.697 --> 18:29.365
Jealous much?

18:33.745 --> 18:35.455
Are you committed?

18:35.622 --> 18:39.209
- Not yet.
- Well, you came to the right place.

18:39.375 --> 18:42.253
Bunch of horny guys, drunk,
ready to pounce.

18:42.420 --> 18:45.340
Ready to mount
anything that moves.

18:45.507 --> 18:46.841
Try, and I'll toss them

18:47.008 --> 18:49.260
