19:02.524 --> 19:05.401
Okay.
Bye-bye, weirdos.

19:10.073 --> 19:11.991
Come on, Noa.

19:34.013 --> 19:36.891
Did you believe one word
from those freaks?

19:43.064 --> 19:44.691
Let go of me!

19:50.780 --> 19:53.950
Well, hello, sexy.
Up for procreating?

19:55.702 --> 19:57.036
Come on.

20:21.436 --> 20:24.063
Excuse me. ls there somewhere
we can go and mate?

20:24.272 --> 20:26.357
Uh, just behind
the tent there.

